data.title: 欢迎来到重生门
data.mainDescriptionZh: 当我们在时光的裂缝中交出旧钥匙，重生门后等待的不仅是新的心跳，更是在对方的瞳孔里遇见第无数次初雪般纯净的相遇。
data.mainTips: 给我进去别瞅啦陈总啊！！！😇
data.mainDescriptiontUs: When we hand over the old keys in the cracks of time, what awaits us behind the door of rebirth is not only a new heartbeat, but also a meeting as pure as the first snowfall seen countless times in each other's pupils.
